Class GlobalObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.musicbox.util.globalobject.GlobalObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MusicRoom, MusicRoomDataContainer, MusicSegment, Track, Variation, VariationTrack, WorkingArea

    public abstract class GlobalObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A global-object can be sent as data over the websocket-protocol from server to client or from client to server. It can be a instance of one of the database-entity-classes.
